The main functionlaties in this experiment is:
1)A dropdown menu to display the languages that are available.
2)When the words are selected,"reform-the-sentence" button is being activated.
3)Once,all the words are selected,"Check the corectness of this sentence" button is activated.
4)After clicking the "reform-the-sentence" button,the words are put back and there would be a chance to reselect them.
5)After clicking the button to get the answers,you will be shown all the possible answers.
6)Besides these features,it would be useful if we get the count of words that we already selected while reforming the sentence.
7)If the answer you submit is wrong,a button that says, "get correct answer" is activated.
